                                Digital Gurus</span>.
                            Based in <span class="bg-brutal-cyan px-1 brutal-border border-2">Rajkot, Gujarat,
                                India</span>.
                        </p>
                        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-gray-600 border-l-4 border-brutal-black pl-4">
                            30+ websites built and maintained. I make WordPress behave and Squarespace look custom.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 reveal-buttons opacity-0 translate-y-8">
